'''輕量化頭盔'''（{{lang-en|'''Lightweight helmet'''}}），簡稱'''LWH頭盔'''（{{lang|en|LWH Helmet}}），是[[美國海軍陸戰隊|美國海軍陸戰隊]]的現役[[戰鬥頭盔|戰鬥頭盔]]，於2004年晚期開始投入使用，至2009年時已完全取代之前使用的[[地面部隊單兵防護系統|PASGT頭盔]]，兩者的外觀在非專業人士眼中差別很小，且在非海軍陸戰隊人員間，仍以PASGT頭盔的綽號「德國佬頭盔」（{{lang|en|Fritz helmet}}）來戲稱之。儘管該款頭盔比[[美國陸軍|美國陸軍]]現役的[[ACH頭盔|ACH頭盔]]重，但因尺寸較大而得以提供更好的保護，重量也仍比PASGT頭盔輕，使用上也比較舒適<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.natick.army.mil/about/pao/pubs/warrior/03/julyaug/index.htm#a2 |title=The Warrior<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2013-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602063340/http://www.natick.army.mil/about/pao/pubs/warrior/03/julyaug/index.htm#a2 |archive-date=2013-06-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

輕量化頭盔的用色是[[橄欖色|橄欖色]]，在外加上[[沙漠|沙漠]]、[[叢林|叢林]]{{Link-en|MARPAT數位迷彩|MARPAT|MARPAT}}[[數位迷彩|數位迷彩]]圖案的{{Link-en|盔套|Helmet cover}}，頭盔前端有托架以便於裝設[[AN/PVS-7夜視鏡|AN/PVS-7夜視鏡]]或[[AN/PVS-14夜視儀|AN/PVS-14]][[單筒望遠鏡|單筒]][[夜視鏡|夜視鏡]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marcorsyscom.usmc.mil/SITES/PMICE/AddInfo/Armor/LWH/LWH%20Sling%20vs%20Pad.pdf|title=Marine Corps Lightweight Helmet: Sling Suspension vs. Padded Suspension|work=Marine Corps Systems Command|publisher=USMC|pages=2|accessdate=2008-07-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090304135039/http://www.marcorsyscom.usmc.mil/SITES/PMICE/AddInfo/Armor/LWH/LWH%20Sling%20vs%20Pad.pdf|archivedate=2009-03-04}}</ref>。後頸部位則加上彈道防護裝置<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.marcorsyscom.usmc.mil/SITES/PMICE/News/Armor/LWH/Extended%20Protection,%20New%20helmet%20pads%20shield%20neck%20from%20fragments.pdf|title=Extended Protection|last=Hoellwarth|first=John|date=March 2007|work=[[Marine_Corps_Times|Marine Corps Times]]|publisher=[[Army_Times_Publishing_Company|Army Times Publishing Company]]|accessdate=2008-07-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090304135009/http://www.marcorsyscom.usmc.mil/SITES/PMICE/News/Armor/LWH/Extended%20Protection%2C%20New%20helmet%20pads%20shield%20neck%20from%20fragments.pdf|archivedate=2009-03-04}}</ref>。

==防彈能力==
以17格令的模擬破片的V50防彈數值為2200英尺/秒(670米/秒)<ref>{{Cite web |title=PURCHASE DESCRIPTION FRAGMENTATION HELMET,LIGHTWEIGHT,USMC |url=https://ciehub.info/spec/PD/FQ-PD-06-35A.pdf |access-date=2021-08-11 |archive-date=2021-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210811201002/https://ciehub.info/spec/PD/FQ-PD-06-35A.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

